name: Bern Weber
note:
Company Name: Smart-HPC 

Company Website:  https://www.continental.com/en/

Contact Person: Bern Weber

Speciality: Motor Vehicle Manufacturing

Country-Location: Germany

Target Audience: worldwide

Company info: Continental develops pioneering technologies and services for sustainable and connected mobility of people and their goods. Founded in 1871, the technology company offers safe, efficient, intelligent and affordable solutions for vehicles, machines, traffic and transportation. In 2022, Continental generated sales of €39.4 billion and currently employs around 200,000 people in 57 countries and markets.

Comment: Bern needs a lead generation manager who can also lead calls in the future. English is important for the client, but also conversational German would be a big plus. The main task will be to correspond via e-mail and also via applications on the website (they have a database of customers to correspond with).
This request is not urgent and he also mentioned that he would be happy to hire 3-4 people. 
We agreed that we would send him all the necessary information about our company and possible candidates that fit his request 

Immediate Requirement: LG (Sales)

Future needs: -

Responsibilities: The main task will be to correspond via e-mail and also via applications on the website (they have a database of customers to correspond with).

Status by the position(s) (possible / impossible): possible

Next Step: send the client our presentation, link to the web-site and suitable CVs

Next Contact Day: Follow up in a week 15th December, to get his feedback.

Planned Start Date: -

The client was engaged by the LG manager 

SM Marina (Diana)



It will be the first call with Smart-HPC


SM Marina ( Diana)
